N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2200.12 - Withdrawal from rental market

State Regulations

Nothing in these regulations shall be construed to
require any person to offer any housing accommodations for rent, but housing
accommodations already on the market may be withdrawn only after an order is
issued by the administrator under section
2204.9
of this Title, if such
withdrawal requires that a tenant be evicted from such
accommodations. Notes
